::KitKat::

She looked at Drillbit. "Well, he called me out.  Just hang on and 
I'll be right back."  She kissed him and looked into his eyes.  She 
handed him her rifle and transformed into wolf mode.  She ran out."I 
accept yourchallenge, you walking peice of slag."  She growled.  She 
had her ears pinned back and her tail down.  the fur on her back was 
up raised and her teeth were bared. She growled loudly at him. 
"Tonight I dine on Maximal." she looked at him and waited for him to 
make the first move.
